<![CDATA[<div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="1"><b style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Please do not respond to this email. This email was sent from an unattended mailbox, and replies are not reviewed. Please instead contact your Staffing representative on {!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}</b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Date: as per date of email</font></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" face="Arial, sans-serif">Dear {!Job_placement__c.Contact__c}</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" face="Arial, sans-serif">1.<br></font></div><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><div><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">I am pleased to be able to offer you a contract of&nbsp;employment with The Challenge Network, which is part of the National Citizen Service programme. Each Wave Contract and each Weekend Contract is a separate employment contract. Each contract is for a fixed term and the beginning and end dates for each fixed term is set out below:</font></span></div><div><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></span></div></blockquote><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Personal Challenge from&nbsp;{!Job_placement__c.PC_KO_Date__c} to&nbsp;{!Job_placement__c.PC_End_date__c},&nbsp;</font></blockquote><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Team Challenge from&nbsp;{!Job_placement__c.TC_KO_date__c} to&nbsp;{!Job_placement__c.TC_end_day__c},&nbsp;</font></blockquote><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Real Challenge Design from&nbsp;<font>{!Job_placement__c.RCD_KO_date__c} to&nbsp;{!Job_placement__c.RCD_End_date__c}&nbsp;("</font><b>Work Period</b>") plus&nbsp;{!Job_placement__c.Annual_Leave_entitlement__c} days ("<b>Holiday Period</b>")];&nbsp;</font></blockquote><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">(a "<b>Wave Contract</b>"),&nbsp;</font></blockquote><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><div><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div></blockquote><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><div><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">and:</font></div></blockquote><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><div><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div></blockquote><blockquote style="margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Real Challenge Action Day 1 on either 07/09/2013 or 08/09/2013,</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Real Challenge Action Day 2 on either 14/09/2013 or 15/09/2013,</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Real Challenge Action Day 3 on either 21/09/2013 or 22/09/2013,</font></div><div><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Real Challenge Action Day 4 on either 28/09/2013 or 29/09/2013, &nbsp;Graduation on either 12/10/2013 or 13/10/2013 &nbsp;("</span><b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Work Period</b>") plus&nbsp;{!Job_placement__c.RCA_Annual_Leave_entitlement__c} days ("<b style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">Holiday Period</b><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">")];&nbsp;</span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">(a &nbsp;"<b>Weekend Contract</b>")</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div></blockquote></blockquote><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">2.&nbsp;</font><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><div><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Although each Wave Contract and each Weekend Contract is a separate contract of employment, please note that if you accept a Wave Contract you must also accept the corresponding Weekend Contract. Similarly you cannot just accept a Weekend Contract without accepting the corresponding Wave Contract. &nbsp;Therefore the offer of the Wave Contract is conditional on your acceptance of the corresponding Weekend Contracts and vice versa, unless specifically agreed otherwise.</font></span></div></blockquote><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">3.<br></font><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><div><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Each employment contract (whether a Wave Contract or a Weekend Contract) is made up from the applicable parts of this email, and The Challenge Network Terms of Employment attached to this email.</font></span></div></blockquote><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">4.<br></font><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><div><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Please note that the Work Period of your contract(s) will be the only time that you will be required to report for work. &nbsp;The Holiday Period of the contract(s) is when you will be expected to take holiday leave. &nbsp;For more information on holiday, please see The Challenge Network Terms of Employment.</font></span></div></blockquote><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">5.<br></font><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><div><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">You cannot start any employment contract with TCN until you have completed the necessary pre employment training applicable to that contract, details of which will be sent to you separately.</font></span></div></blockquote><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">6.<br></font><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><div><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Your role will be {!Job_placement__c.Role__c}.</font></span></div></blockquote><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">7.<br></font><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><div><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Your payment rates and the date of payment for each contract is set out in the &nbsp;Payment Schedule that will be sent to you separately.</font></span></div><div><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Your place of work will be as set out in the Where to be When Guide (‘</span><b style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">WWG</b><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">’). The log in to this portal will be sent to you separately.</span></font></div></blockquote><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">8.<br></font><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><div><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Details of your duties are set out in the Role Guide and who you report to (your "</span><b style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Reporting Manager</b><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">") will be communicated to you prior to the commencement of your role.</span></font></div></blockquote><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">9.<br></font><blockquote style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 0px 40px; border: none; padding: 0px;"><div><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">Your employment cannot commence until we have received (1) two satisfactory references and an enhanced DBS check; (2) a copy of the enclosed terms confirming your acceptance of each contract; and (3) satisfactory evidence that you are not prohibited from working in the UK. &nbsp;Please see the checklist attached to this email for details of what constitutes satisfactory evidence. &nbsp;If you fail to do so you will be unable to commence employment. &nbsp;If this is problematic please contact me for further options.</font></span></div><div><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></span></div></blockquote><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif">To accept your contract(s) please click on the "Yes" button. &nbsp;If you are interested in working with The Challenge Network but do not wish to accept the contract(s) because you want to explore different work schedules please click on the "No, I would like to change my work schedule" button. &nbsp;Should you not wish to accept the contract(s) at all please click on the "No, &nbsp;I do not want to work for The Challenge Network" button.<br><br></font></span></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2">Note: if you do not click on any button by the date that is 7 days before the beginning of the Work Period this offer of employment will lapse and you cannot accept it late, unless The Challenge Network agrees otherwise.</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><span style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><font size="2" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" face="Arial, sans-serif"><img src="http://www.the-challenge.org/email-newsletters/salesforce-templates-2011/images/accept-contract-btn.gif" alt="Yes I accept and hereby sign the contract"></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" face="Arial, sans-serif"><img src="http://www.the-challenge.org/email-newsletters/salesforce-templates-2011/images/change-schedule-btn.gif" alt="No I would like to change my work schedule"></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><font size="2" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);" face="Arial, sans-serif"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"><div><img src="http://www.the-challenge.org/email-newsletters/salesforce-templates-2011/images/no-work-tcn-btn.gif" alt="No,  I do not want to work for The Challenge Network"></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Yours sincerely,</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&nbsp;</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">{!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate__c}</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">For and on behalf of The Challenge Network</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">e: {!Job_placement__c.Staffing_Associate_email__c}</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2.1/SW</font></div><div><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br></font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div>]]></td>
